TY  - JOUR
T1  - Computer Simulation of Peak Hour Operations in a Bus Terminal
AU  - Jennings, Norman H.
AU  - Dickins, Justin H.
Y1  - 1958/10/01
PY  - 1958
DA  - 1958/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.5.1.106
